	   <tr><td colspan=2>One place I found that it actually worked was GD, near the Tizmak caves.&nbsp;&nbsp;I Soothed one mob and pulled the other (who was standing 10 feet away).  I beat it down, then rested for a bit before pulling the other.<br><br>Just a thought; maybe it reduces the assist range rather than the aggro range?  *shrug*  I honestly don't know.  I just learned that Soothe pulling could save me and my mage friend some serious downtime once I found out about it.<br>&nbsp;<br>Dalantia Dragonet<br>Aiyeka's Beloved Guardian, 41st Rank<br>Fennin Ro<br>Kings of Brotherhood</td></tr>
